  <h2>Sunlight requirements</h2>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-12">
      <p>Succulents generally need 6 hours of sunlight per day. They prefer indirect sunlight because direct sunlight can sunburn them.
      Make sure you succulents get enough light per day otherwise their shape will start to change. </p>
